summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Frank E. Scheertzer a bachelor, and William J. Schertzer, a bachelor, to the City of Seattle, dated the 16th day of September, 1909, to a certain portion of Block Nine (9) Yesler's & McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle, also a portion of Block 11 and 12 McKenzie & Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition to the City of Seattle.
